cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.DB, cs.CY, cs.SI 

The paper focuses on developing a personalized recommendation system for C2C e-commerce, which involves machine learning techniques for building and training topic models and classification models. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including Information Retrieval (cs.IR) for the recommendation system, Machine Learning (cs.LG) for the techniques used, Database (cs.DB) for the NoSQL data-based approach, Cybersecurity (cs.CY) for the potential security implications of the system, and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) for the C2C e-commerce context.
